## Lint Commands
```bash
uv run ruff check .          # Python linting (ruff>=0.9 configured in pyproject.toml)
cd frontend && pnpm lint     # ESLint
cd frontend && pnpm typecheck  # TypeScript type check
```

New work should extend existing phases, not introduce new phase ordering constraints.
